query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 10 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('clojure',
'data-structures',
'database-design',
'hadoop',
'matlab',
'memory-leaks',
'networking',
'parsing',
'pip',
'razor',
'recursion',
'vector',
'webpack');
